<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Trust Center</title>
<link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/5.15.4/css/all.min.css">
<style>
    body {
        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
    }
    header {
        background-color: #0078D4;
        color: #fff;
        padding: 10px 20px;
        text-align: center;
    }
    h1 {
        margin: 20px 0;
    }
    .container {
        max-width: 800px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 20px;
    }
    ul {
        list-style-type: none;
        padding: 0;
    }
    ul li {
        padding: 10px 0;
    }
</style>
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <h1>Trust Center</h1>
    </header>
    <div class="container">
        <h2>Security</h2>
        <p>Learn about the security practices and protocols we use to protect your data.</p>
        <h2>Privacy</h2>
        <p>Understand how we collect, use, and protect your personal information.</p>
        <h2>Compliance</h2>
        <p>See our certifications and compliance with industry standards and regulations.</p>
        <h2>Contact Us</h2>
        <p>If you have questions or concerns about our trust center or practices, please contact us.</p>
        <ul>
            <li><i class="fas fa-envelope"></i> Email: contact@yourcompany.com</li>
            <li><i class="fas fa-phone"></i> Phone: 123-456-7890</li>
        </ul>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
